maml:description.maml:para: Creates base64 string needed for APi Call Authorization Token.
Creates base64 string needed for APi Call Authorization Token. Value can be passed to other other cmdlets, but is also stored in global variable CwAuthString

command:example.maml:title: -------------------------- Example 1 --------------------------
command:example.dev:code: PS C:\> $AuthString = New-CwmAuthString -CwCompany 'mycompany' -CwPublicKey 'mypublickey' -CwPrivateKey 'myprivatekey' PS C:\> $Companies = Get-CwmCompany -AuthString $AuthString

dev:remarks.maml:para: Creates AuthString and uses it to query all Companies.
